casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff,
v.
Jason E. MCKINNON, a/k/a Jason E. Morris, Defendant. State of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Gary Maddox, a/k/a Gary Foster, Defendant-Petitioner. C-792 September Term 2017
080440 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005751-14 and A-000192-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted and matter is remanded to the trial court to hold oral argument on defendant's petition for post-conviction relief. Jurisdiction is not retained.
